quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  76,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  76,1,be shak ensaan par zamane mein aik aisa waqt bhi aachuka hai ke woh koi cheez qabil zikar nah thi
  76,2,hum ne ensaan ko نطفہٴ makhloot se pedakiya taakay usay aazmayen to hum ne is ko santa daikhta banaya
  76,3,( aur ) usay rasta bhi dikha diya. ( ab ) woh khuwa shukar guzar ho khuwa nashukara
  76,4,hum ne kafiroon ke liye zanjeer aur taoq aur dehakti aag tayyar kar rakhi hai
  76,5,jo naiko car hain aur woh aisi sharaab nosh jaan karen ge jis mein kafoor ki ameezash hogi
  76,6,yeh aik chashma hai jis mein se khuda ke bande pyin ge aur is mein se ( choti choti ) nehrain nikalen ge
  76,7,yeh log nazren poori karte hain aur is din se jis ki sakhti phail rahi hogi khauf rakhtay hain
  76,8,aur bawajood yeh ke un ko khud ta-aam ki khwahish ( aur haajat ) hai faqeero aur yatimon aur qaidyoun ko khelati hain
  76,9,( aur kehte hain ke ) hum tum ko khalis khuda ke liye khelati hain. nah tum se aiwz ke khawastgah hain nah shkrgzari ke ( tallab-gaar )
  76,10,hum ko apne perwar-digaar se is din ka dar lagta hai ( jo cheharon ko ) kareeha al manzar aur ( dilon ko ) sakht ( muztir kar dainay wala ) hai
  76,11,to khuda un ko is din ki sakhti se bachale ga aur taazgee aur khush dili inayat farmaiye ga
  76,12,aur un ke sabr ke badlay un ko bahisht ( ke baagaat ) aur resham ( ke malbosaat ) ataa kere ga
  76,13,un mein woh takhton par takiye lagaye baithy hon ge. wahan nah dhoop ( ki hiddat ) dekhen ge nah sardi ki shiddat
  76,14,un se ( samardar shaakhen aur ) un ke saaye qareeb hon ge aur meoon ke guchay jhuke hue latak rahay hon ge
  76,15,Khudam ) chandi ke basan liye hue un ke ird gird phrin ge aur sheeshay ke ( nihayat shafaaf ) glass
  76,16,aur sheeshay bhi chandi ke jo theek andazay ke mutabiq banaye gay hain
  76,17,aur wahan un ko aisi sharaab ( bhi ) pilayi jaye gi jis mein sonth ki ameezash hogi
  76,18,yeh bahisht mein aik chashma hai jis ka naam Salsabeel hai
  76,19,aur un ke paas larke atay jatay hon ge jo hamesha ( aik hi haalat par ) rahen ge. jab tum un par nigah daalo to khayaal karo ke bikhare hue moti hain
  76,20,aur bahisht mein ( jahan ) aankhh uthao ge kasrat se Nemat aur azeem ( al shan ) saltanat dekho ge
  76,21,un ( ke badnon ) par Deeba sabz aur Atlas ke kapray hon ge. aur inhen chandi ke kangon pahnaye jayen ge aur un ka perwar-digaar un ko nihayat pakeeza sharaab pilaaye ga
  76,22,yeh tumhara sila aur tumhari koshish ( khuda ke haan ) maqbool hui
  76,23,ae Mohammad ( ) hum ne tum par quran aahista aahista nazilkiya hai
  76,24,to apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke mutabiq sabr kiye raho aur un logon mein se kisi bad amal aur nashukray ka kaha nah manu
  76,25,aur subah vsham apne perwar-digaar ka naam letay raho
  76,26,aur raat ko barri raat taq sjday karo aur is ki paki bayan karte raho
  76,27,yeh log duniya ko dost rakhtay hain aur ( qayamat ke ) bhaari din ko pas pusht chhorey dete hain
  76,28,hum ne un ko pedakiya aur un ke maqabil ko mazboot banaya. aur agar hum chahain to un ke badlay un hi ki terhan aur log le ayen
  76,29,yeh to nasiyaat hai. jo chahay apne perwar-digaar ki taraf pounchanay ka rasta ikhtiyar kere
  76,30,aur tum kuch bhi nahi chaah satke magar jo khuda ko Manzoor ho. be shak khuda jan-nay wala hikmat wala hai
  76,31,jis ko chahta hai apni rehmat mein daakhil karleta hai aur zaalmon ke liye is ne dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
